welcome_message_body: Welcome to beautiful Lake Mary, where southern charm meets modern convenience! Enjoy our pristine lakes, charming downtown area, and endless activities. We can't wait for you to explore and fall in love with our city.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Orlando Sanford International Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Orlando Sanford International Airport serves mainly international flights.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Orlando Executive Airport serves both commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is dedicated to private flights and offers exclusive amenities for private jet travelers.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

terminals.name: Private Terminal

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Orlando International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Terminal

terminals.name: South Terminal
